# Handle line endings automatically for files detected as text
# and leave binary files untouched.
* text=auto

# Explicitly declare text files to always use LF (Unix-style) on checkout?
# Actually, for a Windows-first CLI, 'auto' is safest.
# It converts to CRLF on Windows checkouts and LF on Linux checkouts.

# Deny checkout if we accidentally committed binary files as text
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.zip binary
